A basic CLI application that searches and downloads YT Music songs

## INSTALLATION

### PyPI

`pip install -U pipyt`

## BASIC USAGE

```
pipyt COMMAND [OPTIONS] INPUT
```

- `pipyt <command> --help` for more helping.

### EXAMPLES

`pipyt find <song_name>`

`pipyt down <url/video_id>`

